Question:
Given 3 numbers A, B and C. Find the greatest number among them

Solution:
class Solution {
  public:
    int greatestOfThree(int A, int B, int C) {
        // code here
        if(A>B && A>C)
            return A;
        else if(B>C && B>A)
            return B;
        else
            return C;
        return 0;
    }
};

Explaination:
*We check the greates number using > opeartor
*Then we return the greatest among the three numbers
